## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="d082a-135">系列がデザイン時と実行時の両方で追加されると、自動的に "既定" の <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.ChartArea> オブジェクト、または [既定] が存在しない場合は <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.ChartAreaCollection> で使用可能な最初のグラフ領域に自動的に割り当てられます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d082a-135">When a series is added at both design time and run time, it is automatically assigned to the "Default" <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.ChartArea> object, or the first available chart area in the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.ChartAreaCollection> if "Default" does not exist.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="d082a-136">系列をプロットしない場合は、このプロパティを長さ0の文字列に設定します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d082a-136">Set this property to a zero-length string if you do not want the series to be plotted.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
  
```vb  
' Create a new legend and associate three series with the legend.  
Public Sub CreateSecondLegend()  
    ' Attach the first series to a chart area.  
    Chart1.Series["Series1"].ChartArea = "Chart Area 1";  
  
    ' Attach the second series to a chart area.  
    Chart1.Series["Series2"].ChartArea = "Chart Area 2";  
  
End Sub 'CreateSecondLegend  
```  
  
```csharp  
// Create a new legend and associate three series with the legend.  
public void CreateSecondLegend()  
{  
     // Attach the first series to a chart area.  
     Chart1.Series["Series1"].ChartArea = "Chart Area 1";  
  
     // Attach the second series to a chart area.  
     Chart1.Series["Series2"].ChartArea = "Chart Area 2";  
  
}  
```

  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="d082a-220">系列の影の色を取得または設定します。任意の有効な ARGB (アルファ、赤、緑、青) の値にすることができます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d082a-220">Gets or sets the shadow color of a series, which can be to any valid ARGB (alpha, red, green, blue) value.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="d082a-221">アルファ値は、現実的な影効果を実現するために使用できます。影に色の値 "128, 0, 0, 0" を使用してください。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d082a-221">The alpha value can be used to achieve a realistic shadow effect; try using a color value of "128,0,0,0" for shadows.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="d082a-222">影を実装するには、<xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Series.ShadowOffset%2A> プロパティをゼロ (0) 以外の値に設定します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d082a-222">To implement a shadow, set the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Series.ShadowOffset%2A> property to a value other than zero (0).</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
  
```  
' Set series shadow color and offset  
Public Sub SetSeriesShadow()  
     Chart1.Series("Default"}.ShadowColor = Color.Blue  
     Chart1.Series("Default"}.ShadowOffset = 2  
End Sub 'SetSeriesShadow  
```  
  
```csharp  
// Set series shadow color and offset   
public void SetSeriesShadow()  
{      
    Chart1.Series("Default"}.ShadowColor = Color.Blue;  
    Chart1.Series["Default"].ShadowOffset = 2;  
}  
```
